.IR VAL " | " "mcast_probes VAL " " | "
.B anycast_delay
.IR MSEC " | "
.B proxy_delay
.IR MSEC " | " "proxy_queue LEN " " | "
.B locktime
.IR MSEC " }"

.ti -8
.BR "ip ntable show" " [ "
.B dev
.IR DEV " ] [ "
.B name
.IR NAME " ]"

.SH DESCRIPTION
.I ip ntable
controls tha parametas fo' tha neighbour tables. 

.SS ip ntable show - list tha ip neighbour tables

This commandz displays neighbour table parametas n' statistics.

.TP
.BI dev " DEV"
only list tha table attached ta dis device.

.TP
.BI name " NAME"
only lists tha table wit tha given name.

.SS ip ntable chizzle - modify table parameter

This command allows modifyin table parametas like fuckin timers n' queue lengths.
.TP
.BI name " NAME"
the name of tha table ta modify.

.TP
.BI dev " DEV"
the name of tha thang ta modify tha table joints.

.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
ip ntable show dev eth0
.RS 4
Shows tha neighbour table (IPv4 ARP n' IPv6 ndisc) parametas on thang eth0.
.RE
.PP
ip ntable chizzle name arp_cache queue 8 dev eth0
.RS 4
Changes tha number of packets queued while address is bein resolved from the
default value (3) ta 8 packets.
.RE

